{"tid":579791,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個世界，就算你知足，自己做自己野，都要玩謝你","createTime":"2018-03-04T02:35:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T03:56:04.000Z","uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"078ab669ccc5421672c3453c3e4fc58effb1bf24","tid":579791,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T02:35:23.000Z","msg":"你與世無爭，唔代表個世界對你冇要求<br />\n後生個陣成日諗，究竟自己衰咩<br />\n想揾自己既路，改善自己，尋找快樂<br />\n但人大左出左身咁耐<br />\n錯既原來唔係自己<br />\n如果你未夠薑未ready話錯既係個世界<br />\n起碼都要承認你同個世界係錯配、八字唔夾<br />\n就算你做返自己，個世界都要懲罰你<br />\nThis world will punish you for just being yourself, for who you are.<br />\n人生係冇希望架喇，唔好再呃自己<br />\n得罪講句，跳樓班友就係仲有希望先至跳樓<br />\n樂觀、正能量同食白粉一樣<br />\n終有一日俾佢玩返轉頭"},{"pid":"20abb197c8168ffe879e317155cb3c1bc62f4572","tid":579791,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T03:44:07.000Z","msg":"錯了嗎 後悔了嗎"},{"pid":"4f8a74492a374b4f63c4deb37277989ae1fb07df","tid":579791,"uid":165482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20abb197c8168ffe879e317155cb3c1bc62f4572","tid":579791,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T03:44:07.000Z","msg":"錯了嗎 後悔了嗎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T03:45:26.000Z","msg":"出世已經是個錯誤"},{"pid":"74e795179436236e03d2b03bf20a4c7db09d3bd9","tid":579791,"uid":91884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T03:55:31.000Z","msg":"買英國樓放租比啲學生 夠平<br />\n有需要時<br />\n樓價升 英磅升 再套現 <br />\n每個月收租 fatfat"},{"pid":"ac58cb97a15f891348c064c49a7ca92949fe53c7","tid":579791,"uid":91884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74e795179436236e03d2b03bf20a4c7db09d3bd9","tid":579791,"uid":91884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T03:55:31.000Z","msg":"買英國樓放租比啲學生 夠平<br />\n有需要時<br />\n樓價升 英磅升 再套現 <br />\n每個月收租 fatfat"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T03:56:04.000Z","msg":"覆錯post自膠"}]}